---
alwaysApply: true
---

Always use LLMClient (backend/services/llm_client.py) for all AI calls.
Never import anthropic, openai, or ollama SDKs directly in agent files.

Agents run sequentially. Never introduce parallel or concurrent agent execution.

All pipeline progress must be communicated to the frontend via SSE.
Never use polling as an alternative.

FastAPI route handlers must be async. No synchronous blocking calls in route handlers.